When should I head back
to Superbia...?

from the Superbian Imperial shipyards.
Welcome, mo!

Sold to our Invidian friend over there, mo!
Don't forget the Salvager's Code!

Ah, what a fine day for salvaging!
This is delicious, mo!
Need something, mo?
I'm so tired, mo...
No problem, mo!
Invidian friends, this way, mo!
Taking this up on the elevator, mo!

This looks valuable, mo.

Welcome, mo!
Take a look around, mo.

Would you care for
a delicious sweet, mo?
Why not become a salvager, mo?

Ahh, Avaritia's famous Samo!
This is the stuff!
I'll get some more to take home.
Mo!
Project from your diaphragm, mo!
Stamina is the foundation of commerce, mo!
Moooo!

Grow big and strong, mo~

Mmm...

I've been completely captivated
by that beautiful voice, mo.

goodies in there! My salvager-senses are tingling!

into any part of the Cloud Sea, right?

Nah, you go. You're always bragging about your sword skills.
You first!

We'll go in after the Driver and Blade.
For all we know, this place is a monster nest.

Yeah... Better leave the fighting to the pros.
To each their own, right?
